---

<section class="border-b border-border py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">What Gunawardana Motors gained</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">A two-location dealership in Sri Lanka running on UHADEV DMS.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-600 md:text-4xl" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">60%</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-text">Less admin time</div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-text-secondary/60">Switched from paper to digital</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-600 md:text-4xl" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">25 to 5</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-text">Minutes per invoice</div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-text-secondary/60">Five times faster than before</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-white p-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-600 md:text-4xl" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">2</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-text">Locations, one system</div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-text-secondary/60">Shared data across both sites</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-12">
        <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10H14.017zM0 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151C7.563 6.068 6 8.789 6 11h4v10H0z" />
        </svg>
        <blockquote class="mt-4 text-xl leading-relaxed text-text md:text-2xl">
          Invoicing went from 20 to 30 minutes down to 5 minutes. We see sales, inventory, and outstanding balances across both locations from one dashboard.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dthx4fxte/image/upload/w_48,h_48,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto/v1784069813/ChatGPT_Image_Mar_25_2026_10_45_50_AM_iwl3xg_gwqeq8.png" alt="Gunawardana Motors" class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full object-cover" />
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Gunawardana Motors</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-secondary">TMR Trading Lanka, Embilipitiya</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
